    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Vargr APC Tank</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>4/6 (Wheeled)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>240 ICE</color></b>\n\nThe Vargr, meaning \"Wolf\" in Old Norse, is a large APC with a seven-ton infantry bay and substantial armor protection. This allows it to carry a significant number of troops to the battlefield and deliver them safely.\n\nAs a transport vehicle, the Vargr is relatively lightly armed, with only two Machine Guns and two Medium Lasers in a turret. However, this is sufficient to provide supporting fire for its infantry payload and defend itself from enemy attacks.",
